FUN CONFIG BY NEONOXD aka dbW.
==================
This config is for the hosts of local servers

Video: [Click Here](http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=fuHnvNULoWY "Video")

With this script you can slay people, spawn props, set player gravity, speed, health, make CT win etc.
### Installation
Put the files to cfg folder.
dbw_help to console for the list of the commands and binds etc.
#### Binds
Alt+Numpad - select props

Mouse wheel down - spawn selected prop

Z - Delete prop you are looking at.

And more..
